1 All receipts from the proceeds from the commercialization of intellectual property
2 created through the public-private partnership created under Sections 1 to 5 of this Act
3 shall be deposited into the ibogaine research and intellectual property fund established
4 in Section 2 of this Act. Expenditures from the fund shall be used only for programs or
5 research benefitting at-risk populations that suffer from conditions treatable with
6 ibogaine, including but not limited to opioid use disorder, co-occurring substance use
7 disorder, post-traumatic stress disorder, traumatic brain injury, and other neurological
8 or mental health disorders.
